text: == Events == * Harald I becomes King of England. * Harthacanute becomes king of Denmark. * Magnus I becomes king of Norway. * William II (the future William I of England) becomes duke of Normandy. * Construction on the cathedral of Saint Sabino begins in Bari. * Koper is awarded town rights. == Deaths == * 1 July–3 July — Robert I Duke of Normandy at Bythinian Nicaea while on pilgrimage * October 18 — Sancho III of Navarre * November 4 — Jaromír, duke of Bohemia * November 12 — Canute the Great, King of England, of Denmark, of Norway, some of Sweden, and the territories near the legendary Jomsviking stronghold Jomsburg.
